【一屋·两人·三餐·四季】
Circuit Breaker SG | Baking Time
🕞 Muffins 🧁🧁
Homemade muffins are so much better than anything at your corner cafe. 
I never bake, but this lockdown made me do. And when I bake, I bake them all.

From the classic to go Blueberry Muffins,
the Chocolate Chips Muffins which we want to wake up to every morning,and for chocolate lovers, Double Chocolates Chips Muffins falling for all choc-o-holics. 
These muffins are just heavenly. They are so moist, fluffy and soft. You will love them all.
⚠️: Stay Home, Stay Safe, Stay Healthy
